{"tid":838302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京警告美國 對台軍售必將自食惡果","createTime":"2018-09-27T04:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T04:42:54.000Z","uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4baf95bc0514b070da2e4675ddff931197fd6e9f","tid":838302,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 美國政府昨日宣布，將向台灣出售約值3.3億美元的武器裝備。對此，北京國台辦今日（9月26日）表示堅決反對美國以任何藉口向台灣售武，強調任何挾洋自重的行徑，必食惡果。<br />\n<br />\n北京國台辦發言人安峰山表示，中國外交部與國防部都已表明嚴正立場：堅決反對台灣與美國，進行任何形式的官方往來和軍事聯繫，並且堅決反對美國以任何藉口對台售武，強調任何挾洋自重、破壞台灣和平穩定的行徑，都必將自食惡果。"},{"pid":"4ace365efaf041bbe3ceb41d1cad1f38da1e2fa6","tid":838302,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:25:17.000Z","msg":"又要亮劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c717c5f05a1063e2da22339035243f46d715b603","tid":838302,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:26:49.000Z","msg":"又要收買多d非洲窮撚?"},{"pid":"2c1123dc33117fff922b42dc6a5215be65f97f5f","tid":838302,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:28:03.000Z","msg":"咩果先，咁多年中國對台灣都食白果喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91499c701ee2c07c99ab139611c6e367fbd0b8c8","tid":838302,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:42:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}